nodes.text: It is long past time that the airlines treat passengers, their primary source of income, as customers they cherish and not the nuisance we've become.
Feedback Commenter (164): It is long past time that the airlines treat passengers, their primary source of income, as customers they cherish and not the nuisance we've become.
Annot: It is long past time that the airlines treat passengers, their primary source of income, as customers they cherish and not the nuisance we've become.
It has been said that new fees and penalties will only be passed to the passenger already struggling with higher fares and convenience fees of all kinds.
Feedback Commenter (164): It has been said that new fees and penalties will only be passed to the passenger already struggling with higher fares and convenience fees of all kinds.
Annot: It has been said that new fees and penalties will only be passed to the passenger already struggling with higher fares and convenience fees of all kinds.
Passengers need to remember that the airlines are still a competitive environment.
Feedback Commenter (164): Passengers need to remember that the airlines are still a competitive environment.
Annot: Passengers need to remember that the airlines are still a competitive environment.
If you don't like the fare, go elsewhere or fine some other mode of transportation.
Feedback Commenter (164): If you don't like the fare, go elsewhere or fine some other mode of transportation.
Annot: If you don't like the fare, go elsewhere or fine some other mode of transportation.
Southwest has been a shining example of what the legacy airlines should look forward to if they don't treat customers right.
Feedback Commenter (164): Southwest has been a shining example of what the legacy airlines should look forward to if they don't treat customers right.
Annot: Southwest has been a shining example of what the legacy airlines should look forward to if they don't treat customers right.
I've also found plenty of international airlines far more willing to treat me well on those coveted long haul flights
Feedback Commenter (164): I've also found plenty of international airlines far more willing to treat me well on those coveted long haul flights
Annot: I've also found plenty of international airlines far more willing to treat me well on those coveted long haul flights
and have completely refused to fly any American airlines on a long haul out of the country as a result.
Feedback Commenter (164): and have completely refused to fly any American airlines on a long haul out of the country as a result.
Annot: and have completely refused to fly any American airlines on a long haul out of the country as a result.
They've lost my business
Feedback Commenter (164): They've lost my business
Annot: They've lost my business
and until they lose more, they may never learn.
Feedback Commenter (164): and until they lose more, they may never learn.
Annot: and until they lose more, they may never learn.
They should be allowed to go out of business and let someone else without the legacy problems to have a go at it.
Feedback Commenter (164): They should be allowed to go out of business and let someone else without the legacy problems to have a go at it.
Annot: They should be allowed to go out of business and let someone else without the legacy problems to have a go at it.
American consumers deserve better.
Feedback Commenter (164): American consumers deserve better.
Annot: American consumers deserve better.
Until then, it's Air France or Lufthansa for me!
Feedback Commenter (164): Until then, it's Air France or Lufthansa for me!
Annot: Until then, it's Air France or Lufthansa for me!
As a frequent traveler, I would welcome the rule requiring 24 hour refundability of fares + all fees.
Mpogoda(441): As a frequent traveler, I would welcome the rule requiring 24 hour refundability of fares + all fees.
Annot: As a frequent traveler, I would welcome the rule requiring 24 hour refundability of fares + all fees.
Additionally, there should be a certain window,
Mpogoda(441): Additionally, there should be a certain window,
Annot: Additionally, there should be a certain window,
say, 3 days prior to flying where you should be able to cancel your flight without penalty and receive a refund or at least the ability to change your itinerary without fee.
Mpogoda(441): say, 3 days prior to flying where you should be able to cancel your flight without penalty and receive a refund or at least the ability to change your itinerary without fee.
Annot: say, 3 days prior to flying where you should be able to cancel your flight without penalty and receive a refund or at least the ability to change your itinerary without fee.
As I always say to all who will listen,
Mpogoda(441): As I always say to all who will listen,
Annot: As I always say to all who will listen,
the airline model is one of the worst business models I know of:
Mpogoda(441): the airline model is one of the worst business models I know of:
Annot: the airline model is one of the worst business models I know of:
treat your customers with disdain and make it as inconvenient as possible for them to use your product.
Mpogoda(441): treat your customers with disdain and make it as inconvenient as possible for them to use your product.
Annot: treat your customers with disdain and make it as inconvenient as possible for them to use your product.
Whether it be added fees to check luggage
Mpogoda(441): Whether it be added fees to check luggage
Annot: Whether it be added fees to check luggage
making it too costly to change your itinerary;
Mpogoda(441): making it too costly to change your itinerary;
Annot: making it too costly to change your itinerary;
making it virtually impossible to easily use frequent flyer miles or charging an exorbitant amount to actually use them;
Mpogoda(441): making it virtually impossible to easily use frequent flyer miles or charging an exorbitant amount to actually use them;
Annot: making it virtually impossible to easily use frequent flyer miles or charging an exorbitant amount to actually use them;
not getting timely notice when there are delays to flights
Mpogoda(441): not getting timely notice when there are delays to flights
Annot: not getting timely notice when there are delays to flights
or, even worse, when a flight has been canceled;
Mpogoda(441): or, even worse, when a flight has been canceled;
Annot: or, even worse, when a flight has been canceled;
and lastly, being treated like cattle at the airport and on the plane.
Mpogoda(441): and lastly, being treated like cattle at the airport and on the plane.
Annot: and lastly, being treated like cattle at the airport and on the plane.
Southwest has a pretty good business model;
darawayne(1071): Southwest has a pretty good business model;
Annot: Southwest has a pretty good business model;
they are cheerful and friendly and accommodating.
darawayne(1071): they are cheerful and friendly and accommodating.
Annot: they are cheerful and friendly and accommodating.
And their fares are still mostly bundled.
darawayne(1071): And their fares are still mostly bundled.
Annot: And their fares are still mostly bundled.
When the airlines changed their business model they reduced service AND increased fares, they just claimed they were trying to be fairer to the customers.
darawayne(1071): When the airlines changed their business model they reduced service AND increased fares, they just claimed they were trying to be fairer to the customers.
Annot: When the airlines changed their business model they reduced service AND increased fares, they just claimed they were trying to be fairer to the customers.
And they definitely don't have a cheerful, friendly, accommodating business atmosphere.
darawayne(1071): And they definitely don't have a cheerful, friendly, accommodating business atmosphere.
Annot: And they definitely don't have a cheerful, friendly, accommodating business atmosphere.
I predict that airlines are hastening their own demise when they engage in their anti customer and certainly unethical behavior.
darawayne(1071): I predict that airlines are hastening their own demise when they engage in their anti customer and certainly unethical behavior.
Annot: I predict that airlines are hastening their own demise when they engage in their anti customer and certainly unethical behavior.
